        <p>
          Fan Game Cube transforms how fans experience live sports by enabling them to own virtual zones of actual playing fields through NFTs. These aren't just static collectibles—they're connected to live in-game events as matches unfold in real time.
        </p>
        <p>
          When significant plays occur within specific field zones—a goal scored, a crucial pass completed, a game-changing moment—the NFT holders of those zones earn points and rewards. This creates a direct stake in the action beyond simply cheering from the sidelines.
        </p>
        <p>
