        <h3><strong>How It Works</strong></h3>
        <p>
          The platform's foundation is elegantly simple: real playing fields are divided into virtual zones that fans can purchase as NFTs. Each zone corresponds to actual field positions where gameplay unfolds during live matches.
        </p>
        <p>
          As matches progress, in-game events happening in specific zones—goals scored, plays completed, or key moments—trigger point awards for the NFT holders of those zones. This mechanism creates compelling real-time engagement, as fans watch matches with heightened anticipation, hoping for action in their owned territory.
        </p>
        <p>
          The model's versatility is demonstrated through its growing partnership pipeline. New games are continuously being scheduled with selected partners from over 200 global sports projects. This approach works seamlessly across different sports where field position plays a meaningful role in gameplay and scoring dynamics.
        </p>
        <h3><strong>Key Benefits and Advantages</strong></h3>
